        "faq_question_1": "Is this routine compatible with different skin types?",
        "faq_answer_1": "Yes, it’s formulated to work well across a variety of skin types, including oily, dry, combination, and sensitive skin. If your skin tends to react easily, it’s a good idea to test a small amount first.",
        "faq_question_2": "Can it improve the look of wrinkles or dull skin over time?",
        "faq_answer_2": "This routine focuses on keeping the skin well-moisturized and smooth. With regular use, it can enhance the skin’s overall appearance, helping it look more vibrant and refreshed.",
        "faq_question_3": "Has the product been safety tested?",
        "faq_answer_3": "All formulations are created in line with established cosmetic safety guidelines and undergo testing to ensure they are appropriate for external use. Documentation can be provided when needed.",
        "faq_question_4": "Is it safe to use while pregnant or nursing?",
        "faq_answer_4": "The ingredients are commonly used in skincare, but it’s always best to check with your doctor before adding new products during pregnancy or breastfeeding.",
        "faq_question_5": "Can I pack it in my hand luggage when traveling?",
        "faq_answer_5": "Yes, the capsule design makes it easy to carry while traveling. Since they’re mess-free and not liquid-based, they’re convenient for flights and on-the-go use.",
        "faq_question_6": "Is it suitable to use after physical activity?",
        "faq_answer_6": "Definitely. The single-use capsules are clean and practical, making them ideal after exercise when you want a quick and hygienic skincare step.",
        "faq_question_7": "What are the benefits of capsule packaging?",
        "faq_answer_7": "Capsules provide the right amount for each use, helping avoid waste and keeping the product fresh. They also reduce exposure to air and bacteria, making the routine more hygienic and simple.",
        "faq_question_8": "Where do you currently ship?",
        "faq_answer_8": "We currently deliver within Europe only. Shipping options and delivery times may vary depending on your country and will be shown at checkout.",
